{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/initwithreuseidentifier:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L77","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"symbolKind":"method","title":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)initWithReuseIdentifier:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/initWithReuseIdentifier:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reuseIdentifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"reuseIdentifier","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A unique string identifier for this view that allows you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to reuse this view with multiple similar annotations. You can set this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"parameter to ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if you don’t intend to reuse the view, but it is a good","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"idea in general to specify a reuse identifier to avoid creating redundant","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The initialized annotation view object.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The reuse identifier provides a way for you to improve performance by recycling","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation views as they enter and leave the map’s viewport. As an annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"leaves the viewport, the map view moves its associated view to a reuse queue.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When a new annotation becomes visible, you can request a view for that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation by passing the appropriate reuse identifier string to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","type":"reference"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Initializes and returns a new annotation view object."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/initWithReuseIdentifier:":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/initWithReuseIdentifier:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:"}],"title":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/initwithreuseidentifier:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Initializes and returns a new annotation view object."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"}],"title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}]}}}